    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and it's completely spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
