    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve totally babied this ride, keeping it tucked away in the garage and staying on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. I'm really looking for a smooth, easy sale, so feel free to reach out with any questions. You\u2019ve gotta see this one in person!",
