    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the double-VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis remains taut, riding on original-spec dampers with zero fluid seepage. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic with an immaculate Nappa leather interior, the side bolsters show no signs of compression or wear. The variable M differential lock operates flawlessly, providing optimal traction out of apexes. This is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle with a documented service history, free from any electrolytic corrosion or heat-cycle fatigue in the engine bay.",
